{% comment %}
  Main Product — Milestone 1.

  Scope is deliberately narrow: media, title, vendor, price,
  description, and a real add-to-cart form. No variant picker, no
  quantity selector, no dynamic checkout, no tabs, no related products —
  all explicitly deferred to later milestones.

  Self-contained per the brief: no shared components.css dependency, no
  new snippets, no refactor of existing sections/CSS. Price/badge markup
  is intentionally inline rather than pulled into a snippet — the same
  logic already exists in featured-collection.liquid and
  featured-product.liquid, and extracting a shared snippet now would be
  a refactor, which this milestone explicitly excludes.

  Media: featured image only, not a gallery. Product media becomes
  variant-linked once a variant picker exists, so a static multi-image
  gallery built now would likely need rework in that milestone anyway —
  a single stable image is the safer boundary for this pass.

  Add-to-cart: a real Shopify product form tag wraps the submit button
  /cart/add, not decorative). Uses
  product.selected_or_first_available_variant since there's no variant
  picker yet — this is an honest limitation, not an oversight: a
  multi-variant product can only be purchased as whichever variant that
  resolves to (the first available one, or whichever is set via a
  ?variant= URL parameter) until the variant-picker milestone lands.

  No settings: this milestone's brief listed no "Section Settings", so
  none are invented here — layout and spacing are fixed via tokens
  directly rather than exposed as merchant choices that don't exist yet.
{% endcomment %}

{{ 'main-product.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

{%- liquid
  assign featured_image = product.featured_image
  assign variant = product.selected_or_first_available_variant
  assign compare_at_price = variant.compare_at_price
  assign price = variant.price
-%}

<section class="main-product">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid md:grid--two main-product__grid">
      <div class="main-product__media">
        {%- if featured_image != blank -%}
          {{
            featured_image
            | image_url: width: 1600
            | image_tag:
              loading: 'eager',
              fetchpriority: 'high',
              sizes: '(min-width: 48em) 50vw, 100vw',
              widths: '400,700,1000,1600',
              class: 'main-product__image',
              alt: featured_image.alt | default: product.title | escape
          }}
        {%- else -%}
          <div class="main-product__placeholder" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 120 120" class="main-product__placeholder-mark">
              <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="38" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"/>
              <path d="M60 40v40M40 60h40" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>

      <div class="main-product__content">
        {%- if product.vendor != blank -%}
          <p class="main-product__vendor">{{ product.vendor | escape }}</p>
        {%- endif -%}

        <h1 class="main-product__title">{{ product.title | escape }}</h1>

        <p class="main-product__price">
          {%- if compare_at_price > price -%}
            <span class="main-product__price--sale">{{ price | money }}</span>
            <span class="main-product__compare-price">{{ compare_at_price | money }}</span>
          {%- else -%}
            {{ price | money }}
          {%- endif -%}
        </p>

        {%- if product.description != blank -%}
          <div class="main-product__description">{{ product.description }}</div>
        {%- endif -%}

        {%- form 'product', product, class: 'main-product__form' -%}
          <input type="hidden" name="id" value="{{ variant.id }}">
          <button
            type="submit"
            name="add"
            class="main-product__button"
            {% if variant.available == false %}disabled{% endif %}
          >
            {%- if variant.available -%}
              {{ 'sections.main_product.add_to_cart' | t }}
            {%- else -%}
              {{ 'sections.main_product.sold_out' | t }}
            {%- endif -%}
          </button>
        {%- endform -%}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Product information"
}
{% endschema %}
